description: Lanterns always enhance a home’s decor – and when it gets dark outside, their glow creates a cozy atmosphere.
This twelve-opening collage frame creates a fun wall display, with multiple openings. Share a collection of memories in this unique collage frame. Ready to hang. Holds twelve 4 x 6" photos.
The generous size, low armrests and pocket springs with foam that adapts to the body invites you and your guests to many hours of socialising and relaxation.
You can stack the chairs, so they take less space when you're not using them.
A clean design with solid wood veneer. Place the bed on its own or with the headboard against a wall.
